      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so if we're looking at the \"core\" standards for this guide—like the standard for dress codes, how people should carry themselves in a boardroom, or even how to structure a professional conversation—what would you say are the foundational pillars of sophistication that every global professional should master?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
